{"tid":1521080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［被捕後］IPhone快速暫停FaceID/TouchID功能","createTime":"2019-08-31T05:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:05:24.000Z","uid":44218,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7d32f949493c44083255e8b336e8ca6fa1f37a69","tid":1521080,"uid":44218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"或者大家都聽過人話出去發夢要熄左生物認證，轉返用密碼解鎖，怕警犬會捉住你隻手解鎖手機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用FaceID既就記住千祈要啟動 'Require attention for FaceID'，咁一定要用家眼睛望實屏幕先可鎖到。你畀警犬捉實只要合埋眼就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EoRffmF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEoRffmF.png&h=32bc6b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用TouchID既用家就難搞D，警犬捉實你手指就一定會。所以有個方法大家一定要學，就係<br />\n<br />\n<strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Emergency &amp; SOS 功能</span></span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n只要你一㩒實開關制+其中一個音量制，或者連㩒五下開關制，就會自動打畀999。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係㩒左之後一定會暫停左生物認證，一定要打密碼先可以解鎖到手機！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTouchID 用家：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w55PjTe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw55PjTe.png&h=38934d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFaceID 用家：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkXNQYA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkXNQYA.png&h=5506c5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你仲可以係Emergency Contact度寫低被捕後既律師電話，唔洗再背咩狗不要狗檸狗七狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多iPhone上既安全措施可以做，例如需要解鎖左手機先可以睇Notification / 快速回覆訊息等等。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係熄左 '<span style=\"color: red;\">USB Accessories</span>' 佢，咁你iPhone就唔可以係鎖機期間插條USB access度部手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddL0rAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddL0rAm.png&h=1ea04ada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9acdfa35282b783d6ebd56db0f877815c0a0f7d","tid":1521080,"uid":44218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"88f4dc65a84837a48e9a5e1cd388336c7b0406d4","tid":1521080,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"自動打俾999？"},{"pid":"e0b9050e64906626b781f05d3bd7eb0cdee777c2","tid":1521080,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c172d1a698a808c26e8cb8216c78b3b715e79b45","tid":1521080,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"10f510a801348807b9d036aa40831c88d03acd28","tid":1521080,"uid":44218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88f4dc65a84837a48e9a5e1cd388336c7b0406d4","tid":1521080,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"自動打俾999？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n重點係會即刻要打密碼先可以解鎖手機"},{"pid":"92e8d9c49228c33a5b753712fdeebacde71369ae","tid":1521080,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"da5bd96068739e3d87bb144ec5a8018a0d80b9f1","tid":1521080,"uid":44218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"bdd5b4c8e559d13ab94540663af069474d2bb785","tid":1521080,"uid":7524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"iOS : 撳實lock機制 同減音量制 一齊撳實 3秒<br />\n全部touch ID FACEID 收皮<br />\n要手動打PW"},{"pid":"73df980710e5c26438683812ad29223360ee3af6","tid":1521080,"uid":308402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b69113fcd39fc0be9b608b37adbcc06a8b8bf177","tid":1521080